=Love Me in Three Days=

2
00:00:19,700 --> 00:00:21,780
=Episode 20=

3
00:00:25,080 --> 00:00:25,840
Xia Luoluo!

4
00:00:25,840 --> 00:00:28,040
How dare you meet Shan Chenxing
in private behind Yifan's back?

5
00:00:30,440 --> 00:00:33,080
Yifan, how come it's you?

6
00:00:34,400 --> 00:00:35,280
Who else do you think it is?

7
00:00:37,480 --> 00:00:39,200
What did Xia Luoluo do

8
00:00:41,320 --> 00:00:43,240
that she gets to seduce Yifan?

9
00:00:44,440 --> 00:00:45,920
She's good at that.

10
00:00:47,800 --> 00:00:48,320
Yifan.

11
00:00:48,320 --> 00:00:49,160
Touch me.

12
00:00:49,160 --> 00:00:50,320
No.

13
00:00:50,560 --> 00:00:51,840
Hurry up.

14
00:00:52,680 --> 00:00:53,560
That's not nice.

15
00:00:53,840 --> 00:00:54,880
I'll pull back my investment.

16
00:00:56,720 --> 00:00:57,360
Hand.

17
00:00:58,160 --> 00:01:00,080
You should've told me earlier.

18
00:01:03,800 --> 00:01:04,560
Xuewei,

19
00:01:05,400 --> 00:01:07,120
your tricks are flawed.

20
00:01:07,640 --> 00:01:08,920
It shows that you're actually
not a bad person.

21
00:01:10,120 --> 00:01:11,360
I don't understand
what you're talking about.

22
00:01:26,640 --> 00:01:28,360
I obviously saw Shan Chenxing
going in there,

23
00:01:29,120 --> 00:01:30,880
why did it become Yifan?

24
00:01:31,200 --> 00:01:32,680
Luckily I have my last resort.

25
00:01:48,760 --> 00:01:50,640
(Hurry up, kiss me.)

26
00:01:51,360 --> 00:01:52,080
(Hurry up.)

27
00:01:52,880 --> 00:01:54,280
(Hurry up. Transform back quickly.)

28
00:02:01,440 --> 00:02:03,040
Hello, Madam Zhou.

29
00:02:03,040 --> 00:02:04,600
I've found out how Yifan

30
00:02:04,600 --> 00:02:05,760
is being controlled by Xia Luoluo.

31
00:02:10,240 --> 00:02:11,440
How was my acting just now?

32
00:02:12,440 --> 00:02:13,200
Not bad.

33
00:02:14,360 --> 00:02:16,560
I'll give you

34
00:02:16,560 --> 00:02:17,240
the best actress award.

35
00:02:21,000 --> 00:02:21,920
No.

36
00:02:23,080 --> 00:02:24,440
What do you want then?

37
00:02:31,160 --> 00:02:33,840
I want you to dance Koduck for me.

38
00:02:35,240 --> 00:02:36,560
What's Koduck?

39
00:02:38,680 --> 00:02:40,320
This one.

40
00:02:46,440 --> 00:02:48,160
Will you dance?

41
00:03:11,160 --> 00:03:12,400
I'll kiss you once.

42
00:03:27,940 --> 00:03:32,700
♪The feeling is strange yet familiar♪

43
00:03:32,700 --> 00:03:38,620
♪Like the rainbow's finally here♪

44
00:03:40,440 --> 00:03:41,920
Only one kiss?

45
00:03:48,320 --> 00:03:49,560
What if I want to do

46
00:03:50,320 --> 00:03:51,880
something worse than a kiss?

47
00:03:54,000 --> 00:03:56,350
♪I'm honoured to have met you♪

48
00:03:56,360 --> 00:03:57,240
Is that okay?

49
00:03:57,260 --> 00:04:00,680
♪During the rainy season♪

50
00:04:00,680 --> 00:04:04,720
♪You have wide shoulders♪

51
00:04:04,960 --> 00:04:06,240
I'll take it as a yes
since you're not talking.

52
00:04:07,560 --> 00:04:10,840
♪Keeping you company is an honour♪

53
00:04:10,840 --> 00:04:14,160
♪In this long journey♪

54
00:04:14,160 --> 00:04:19,760
♪Love is shining gently♪

55
00:04:19,760 --> 00:04:23,600
♪In our eyes♪

56
00:04:41,560 --> 00:04:42,280
Breakfast is ready.

57
00:04:44,440 --> 00:04:45,760
Did you rest well?

58
00:04:47,520 --> 00:04:48,160
No.

59
00:04:48,840 --> 00:04:50,400
You were snoring loudly.

60
00:04:51,440 --> 00:04:53,000
You heard that I was snoring?

61
00:04:53,920 --> 00:04:56,520
It means you were not tired enough
last night.

62
00:04:57,400 --> 00:04:58,760
I have to...

63
00:05:00,960 --> 00:05:01,880
I was just saying.

64
00:05:01,880 --> 00:05:02,880
I was just simply saying.

65
00:05:02,880 --> 00:05:03,760
I was wrong.

66
00:05:05,440 --> 00:05:08,160
How should I punish you then?

67
00:05:08,560 --> 00:05:10,400
I learned my mistake and changed.

68
00:05:10,400 --> 00:05:11,560
You should reward me.

69
00:05:12,480 --> 00:05:13,440
How do you know

70
00:05:13,960 --> 00:05:16,640
if the punishment and
the reward are different?

71
00:05:34,920 --> 00:05:36,240
Your phone is ringing.

72
00:05:36,240 --> 00:05:37,520
Pick up the call.

73
00:05:39,840 --> 00:05:41,120
There's nothing more important
than this.

74
00:05:43,880 --> 00:05:44,680
I'm picking it up.

75
00:05:46,000 --> 00:05:47,520
(Mr. Shan, this is bad.)

76
00:05:48,080 --> 00:05:49,720
(Ms. Zhou is holding
the shareholder meeting suddenly)

77
00:05:49,720 --> 00:05:50,920
(to expose your secret.)

78
00:05:50,920 --> 00:05:51,920
Well...

79
00:05:57,680 --> 00:05:59,720
What secret Mr. Shan has

80
00:05:59,720 --> 00:06:00,760
that you had to ask

81
00:06:00,760 --> 00:06:02,680
- everyone of us here?
- That's right.

82
00:06:03,200 --> 00:06:04,440
Don't worry.

83
00:06:04,960 --> 00:06:07,640
When Mr. Shan is here, you'll know.

84
00:06:07,660 --> 00:06:10,980
(Xinge Group)

85
00:06:12,040 --> 00:06:14,200
Hello, Mr. Shan.

86
00:06:21,880 --> 00:06:22,720
Ms. Zhou.

87
00:06:23,600 --> 00:06:24,720
Everyone is here today.

88
00:06:25,560 --> 00:06:26,640
You can tell us what it is

89
00:06:26,880 --> 00:06:28,400
right before us today.

90
00:06:30,920 --> 00:06:32,040
The first thing is that

91
00:06:32,480 --> 00:06:33,320
I announce that

92
00:06:33,320 --> 00:06:36,160
Zhou family will increase
the investment in Xinge Group.

93
00:06:36,840 --> 00:06:38,360
That's a good thing.

94
00:06:44,240 --> 00:06:45,960
Ms. Zhou, thank you for your trust.

95
00:06:46,600 --> 00:06:47,240
Mr. Shan.

96
00:06:47,760 --> 00:06:48,920
I'm looking forward to working with you.

97
00:06:53,180 --> 00:06:54,420
(Shan Yifan, CEO)

98
00:06:54,720 --> 00:06:56,640
Come with me. Mr. Shan
needs you now. Come on.

99
00:06:56,640 --> 00:06:57,480
What happened?

100
00:07:01,040 --> 00:07:02,960
No one can get out from here today.

101
