Mr. Shan, why?

102
00:07:04,760 --> 00:07:06,840
You don't even want to shake hands
with me as a gesture?

103
00:07:18,560 --> 00:07:21,080
Well, Ms. Zhou.
Regarding Mr. Shan's matter,

104
00:07:21,080 --> 00:07:21,880
